text: Jessica Yu Li Henwick (李玉; born 30 August 1992) is an English actress. She is known for her roles as Nymeria Sand in HBO series Game of Thrones (2015–2017), X-wing pilot Jessika Pava in Star Wars: The Force Awakens (2015) and the character Colleen Wing in Iron Fist (2017–2018), The Defenders (2017) and the second season of Luke Cage (2018). ==References== Category:Living people Category:Actors from Surrey Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English child actors Category:1992 births
